                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__grinzing-immo_4"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__wenzel_neunhofer_QGW_II_II_3491"><rs type="person" ref="pe__wenzel_neunhofer_QGW_II_II_3491">Wenczlaben des
